headline.print_headline: Hungary Fight Back to Claim 1-1 Draw in Romania
headline.main: Hungary Fight Back to Claim 1-1 Draw in Romania

lead_paragraph: Balazs Dzsudzsak's perfectly executed free kick gave Hungary welcome relief as they fought back to draw 1-1 at neighbours Romania amid a feverish, feisty affair both on and off the pitch in their Euro 2016 Group F qualifier on Saturday.
